  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p /><p>RepairQ empowers business owners by providing robust accounting and inventory reports tailored to extract essential data for your accounting system. These reports streamline the process of posting data to your accounting software and enhance your ability to make informed decisions based on accurate and detailed financial information.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Efficiency </strong>- Quickly extract crucial data, saving time and effort in manually gathering and inputting information into your accounting system.</p></li><li><p><strong>Accuracy </strong>- Ensure precision in your accounting records by providing detailed reports, reducing the risk of errors associated with manual data entry.</p></li><li><p><strong>Financial Insight</strong> - RepairQ offers a range of reports, including accounting summaries, journal entries, revenue and COGS, inventory usage, inventory valuation, and more.</p></li><li><p><strong>Compliance </strong>- Meet accounting standards and compliance requirements by providing organized and detailed data for your accounting system and/or accountant.</p></li><li><p><strong>Integration</strong> - Our integration with QuickBooks Online allows you to automate the transmission of nightly journal entries, freeing up your time to focus on core business activities. Check out our <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://quickbooks.intuit.com/app/apps/appdetails/repairq/en-us/?queryID=25a61071f60f12e63e6a6ad20cb0ab2e\" rel=\"nofollow\">QuickBooks partner page</a> for more info!</p></li></ul><p>Check out the links below to view tutorials and additional related information.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1934524484/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934360642/RepairQ+Accounting+Principles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934360642\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RepairQ Accounting Principles</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934229563/Integrations+QuickBooks+Online+Setup\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934229563\" data-linked-resource-version=\"19\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrations: QuickBooks Online Setup</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934458970/Chart+of+Accounts+-+Accounting+Journal+Entries\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934458970\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Chart of Accounts - Accounting Journal Entries</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246874/Journal+Entries+Set+Default+Account+Classifications\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933246874\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Journal Entries: Set Default Account Classifications</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246837/Reports+Accounting+Journal+Entries\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933246837\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Accounting Journal Entries</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934393396/QuickBooks+Integration+Sending+Journal+Entries+on+Demand\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934393396\" data-linked-resource-version=\"11\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">QuickBooks Integration: Sending Journal Entries on Demand</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917678/Reports+Accounting+System+Reporting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934917678\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Accounting System Reporting</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933279311/Introduction+to+Taxes+in+RepairQ+-+Start+Here\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933279311\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Introduction to Taxes in RepairQ - Start Here!</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
